text: The Dolomitenlauf is a cross-country skiing marathon in Austria. It was first held in 1970 and has been part of Worldloppet as long as Worldloppet has been around. == References == ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1970 establishments in Europe Category:Skiing Category:Sport in Austria Category:Tyrol (state) Category:1970s establishments in Austria
